{
  "EvelynRepeteable": "Hello, dear!^I was thinking about you today and wanted to send you a little something.^^I hope it brings a bit of joy to your day.^Thank you for being such a wonderful friend.^^With love,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.1": "Hello, dear.^I've noticed how hard you've been working on the farm lately.^While I was tidying up my cupboards, I found these extra seeds.^^I'm sure they'll be much happier growing on your farm.^Just don't forget to get a little rest too.^^With love,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.2": "Hello again!^It always makes me smile to see you walking past our little house.^George says he doesn't mind, but I know he enjoys your visits.^^I picked out these flower bulbs to make your farm even more beautiful.^I hope they bloom just as wonderfully as our friendship.^^With love,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.3": "Dear,^The flowers by my window are blooming, and they made me think of you.^It's such a joy to see our friendship continue to grow.^^I'm sending you some of my favorite seeds.^Take good care of them, and I'm sure they'll fill your farm with happiness.^^With love,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.4": "Hello!^The weather is changing, and the garden needs plenty of care, but there's always time to think about good friends.^^I hope these seeds bring beautiful colors and a lovely fragrance to your farm.^When they bloom, I hope they'll remind you of me.^^A warm hug,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.5": "I hope you're doing well.^I'd been saving this rare seed for a special occasion, but then I realized there couldn't be a better time to thank you for your friendship.^^I also made this dried sunflower arrangement for your home.^I'm sure it will make it feel even cozier.^^With love,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.6": "Hello, dear.^With all the hard work that comes with running a farm, I know you sometimes forget to rest and eat properly.^^So I packed a hearty lunch for you to carry in your backpack today.^Promise me you'll take good care of yourself too, alright?^^A warm hug,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.7": "Dear,^I spent the morning in the kitchen, and the smell of rice pudding made me think of you.^^I packed a serving for you,^along with a little plant I recently repotted.^I'm sure it will look lovely on your porch.^^With love,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.8": "Hello!^Today I made the stuffing George loves so much, and as always, I ended up cooking more than we could eat.^So I saved a nice portion just for you.^^I'm also sending you this plant from my garden.^It changes with the seasons and always makes me smile. I hope it does the same for you.^^A warm hug,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.9": "Dear,^I made a batch of my cranberry candies and saved the very best ones just for you.^^I found this decoration tucked away in an old chest, and I thought it would look perfect in your cozy home.^Thank you for bringing so much happiness to our little town.^^With love,^- Granny Evelyn",
  "evelyn.10": "I can't put into words how much you've changed our lives for the better.^George and I truly think of you as part of our family.^^I baked my very best cake to celebrate, and I also prepared this lovely flower pot for you.^There will always be a warm place waiting for you in our home.^^With all my love,^- Granny Evelyn"
}